text.author: Santa Barbara Corpus of Spoken American English (ed. John W. Du Bois)
text.summary: Some veterinarians discuss various treatments and their pricing for several patients while going about daily business in the office, culminating in one vet, Marcia, calling Carol, the owner of a patient, to discuss further treatment of an animal with a broken leg.
text.title: Vet Morning
